

Quick steps to run a simulation (SDHCALSim repertory)
-----------------------------------------------------
source monInit.sh                                  // Export LCIO, ROOT and GEANT4 directories                                       
bin/SDHCAL_Simu mac/testrun.mac                    // Run a simulation with testrun.mac parameters
-----------------------------------------------------


mv test.000.slcio nom_explicite.slcio                                     
mv nom_explicite.slcio ~/SDHCALSim_debut/Simulations


Quick steps to build the root file (SDHCALSim_debut repertory) 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
gSystem->Load("${LCIO}/lib/liblcio.so");              /*    Load      
gSystem->Load("${LCIO}/lib/liblcioDict.so");                Libraries  */
.x writeTree.C("nom_explicite.slcio")                // Write the root file
.q                                                            
--------------------------------------------------------------------------


mv lcioTree.root nom_explicite.root


Quick steps to start digitisation and make graphs (SDHCALSim_debut repertory)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
gSystem->Load("${LCIO}/lib/liblcio.so");           /*      Load
gSystem->Load("${LCIO}/lib/liblcioDict.so");               Libraries */
gSystem->CompileMacro("DeadTime.C");               // Run Deadtime
calculeExemple(1,9e4,MODELE::EDB)                  // (Rayon mort ,Temps mort, modele (RTM/EDB/NP/BDM) )
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------


dumpevent ../SDHCALSim_debut/Simulations/slcio/450_kaons_100_runs_1e7.slcio 1 | less    // Read slcio file
.x RayonTempsmort.C                                                                     // Dead time in function of dead radius to reproduce efficacity graphs
